edu.ucsc.cross.hse.core.monitors

Class EngineSupervisor

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucsc.cross.hse.core.monitors.EngineSupervisor

  • public class EngineSupervisor
extends java.lang.Object
    The main interface between all of the processing and monitoring components that perform tasks and run the environment. Intended Operator: System
